                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mt-4">At scale, this becomes the main revenue engine.</p>
                    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-700">Take
                        <span class="block text-6xl font-extrabold text-indigo-600 my-2">0.35% – 0.45%</span>
                        of payment volume processed through EatGo.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

